Popular skit maker Adebowale Adedayo aka Mr Macaroni has stated no politician offers Nigerians anything by being in office.   I’d rather die than fight over a man – Caramel     Mercy Aigbe’s husband breaks silence, says I’ve two…     I will deal with any girl who tries to hurt my sons –…   Mr Macaroni has been advocating for good governance through his skits and pronouncements lately. The 29-year-old comedian tweeted on Tuesday: “No politician is doing the Citizens a favor by being in office. The concept of leadership is service, selflessness and sacrifice. The people must unite and stop fighting themselves.”